Citation.sTitle: Densities and Viscosities of Niacin + 3-Picoline + Sulfuric Acid + Water from (293.15 to 343.15) K
Citation.sAbstract: The densities and viscosities of niacin + 3-picoline + sulfuric acid + water mixtures have been determined experimentally at temperatures from 293.15 K to 343.15 K. The apparent molar volumes of niacin were calculated from experimental measurements. Results were fitted to obtain the adjustable parameters and standard deviations between the measured and fitted values.
